---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for QuizNiva."
  currentPath="/privacy-policy"
>
  <section class="page-intro section">
    <p class="eyebrow">Privacy</p>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: May 19, 2026</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section prose prose--standalone">
    <h2>Information We Store</h2>
    <p>
      QuizNiva does not require an account in the first version. Quiz progress, best scores, attempts, and last visited topic may be stored in your browser using localStorage.
    </p>

    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      Basic analytics may be added later to understand page views, quiz starts, quiz completions, and popular topics. Sensitive personal information should not be collected for quiz practice.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies And Advertising</h2>
    <p>
      The first version does not include advertising. If advertising partners are added later, cookies or similar technologies may be used according to the partner policy and applicable law.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      For privacy questions, contact the site owner at
      <a class="text-link" href="mailto:contact@quizniva.in">contact@quizniva.in</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
